 melt <b>2 min\/50°C\/speed 3<b>. Drizzle roulade with melted chocolate. Place into refrigerator to chill for approx. 30 minutes. Remove from refrigerator 15 minutes before slicing and serving. ","step":9}],"usefulItems":"deep-sided baking tray, baking paper, bowl, serving platter, oven, refrigerator","id":"r114669","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-5XpB-YXk3og\/XZWfl4Idr_I\/AAAAAAAAfHA\/Tt5DeWwFH9c-V42seYJMKlwiVukimulqwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_yQoeTITV5nx2npe1.png","title":"Hazelnut meringue roulade","ingredients":[{"isHeader":true,"content":"Ingredients"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"100 g hazelnuts, roasted and skin removed"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"4 egg whites"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 pinch cream of tartar"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"200 g caster sugar"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 tsp natural vanilla extract"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"300 g pouring (whipping) cream"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"310 g tinned mandarin segments, drained"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"60 g dark chocolate (gluten free), broken into pieces"}],"nutrition":["per 1 portion","2090 kJ \/ 497 kcal","7.5 g","45.1 g","32.5 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["You can replace tinned mandarin segments with drained tinned fruit of choice or fresh strawberries."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","1h 30m","6 portions"]}